duck: overcome definition: to get the better of.
Overcome (Alexandra Burke album) - Overcome is the debut studio album by British pop/R&B singer Alexandra Burke, released October 19, 2009 on Syco Music.
Overcome (All That Remains album) - Overcome is the fourth studio album by American metalcore band, All That Remains.
"Overcome" (Creed song) - "Overcome" is a song written and performed by Creed.
"Overcome" (Live song) - "Overcome" is a song by alternative rock group Live, which was released as the second single from their 2001 album, V.
